        <div class="msgSubject">Do chat entry limits pose a problem?</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-09-26 23:00:48   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1285563648215006832" id="quote-1285563648215006832" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1285563648215006832" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=152&amp;mid=1285563648215006832&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1285563648215006832&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1285563648215006832" onclick="followToggle('add','1285563648215006832')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
